# TaskPulse

TaskPulse is an AI-powered task prioritization system designed to help individuals and teams focus on what matters most.

Unlike traditional to-do lists, TaskPulse continuously analyzes task urgency, importance, estimated effort, and user productivity habits to generate a dynamic priority score.

## Features


* Python
* FastAPI
* PostgreSQL
* Redis
* Docker
* React Dashboard

## Example Use Case

A software development team can use TaskPulse to automatically identify critical tasks that are at risk of missing deadlines and redistribute workloads accordingly.

